These directores contains the MLN formulae (pml files) used in the paper:
"Collective Semantic Role Labelling with Markov Logic" submited to the Open 
Track of the CoNLL 2008 Shared Task.

Directories:
full      : Full system
up        : Top-down formulae is commented. It resembles a bottom-up system.
downi     : Bottom-up formulae is commented. It resembles a top-down system.
isolated  : Both, Top-down and bottom-up formulae are commented. There are not
    structural relation between predicates.
structural: Without additional global formulae, only structural.

Note:
 The predicates hasRole and sense which are mention in the paper, appear on 
 these files as, hasLabel and frameLabel.

Descriptions of pml files:
 model1.pml                 : Main pml file
 model1-frameLabel.pml      : Main pml for the frameLabel predicate
 model1-hasLabel.pml        : Main pml for the hasLabel predicate
 model1-isArgument.pml      : Main pml for the isArgument predicate
 model1-isPredicate.pml     : Main pml for the isPredicate predicate
 model1-role.pml            : Main pml for the role predicate
 frameLabel-global.pml      : Soft global formulae for the frameLabel predicate
 frameLabel-hard.pml        : Hard structural formulae for the frameLabel
                              predicate
 frameLabel-local.pml       : Local formulae for the frameLabel predicate
 hasLabel-basic.pml         : Local formulae for the hasLabel predicate (close
                              track predicates)
 hasLabel-dep.pml           : Local formulae for the hasLabel predicate (open
                              predicates)
 hasLabel-hard.pml          : Hard structural formulae for hasLabel pedicate

 isArgument-hard.pml        : Hard structural formulae for isArgument predicate
 isArgument-local.pml       : Local formulae for isArgument predicate
 isPredicate-hard.pml       : Hard structural formulae for isPredicate predicate
 isPredicate-local.pml      : Local formulae for isPredicate predicate
 role-simple.pml            : Local formulae for role predicate (close track
                               predicates)
 role-path.pml              : Local formulae for role predicate (depency parses
                              predicates)
 role-hard.pml              : Hard structural formulae for role predicate.
 role-pp-attach.pml         : Local formulae for prepositiona attachment for the
                              role predicate (unused).
 
 
 role-dep.pml, role-basic.pml, isArgument-global.pml, model1-both.pml, 
 model1-dep.pml, dep-bigram.pml, dep-malt.pml, init.pml, inspect.pml, 
 scratch.pml, scratch-whole.pml, seb-inspect.pml, test.pml, train.pml
 types.pml aren't used for these models.



